comments: Does noun trash invoke roleset trash-01?
impatient-01 is a roleset in PropBank, but wasn't suggested in AMR Editor. I decided to use it. Ref: https://propbank.github.io/v3.4.0/frames/impatient.html#impatient.01

cause-01 was added as an argument of :time instead of as an argument of arrive-01. ‘The policeman were coming from so far away’ is the reason for the firemen arriving after the police, not the reason for them arriving at all.
Because they are fifteen I put the reentrancy on the 'and'.
